Interface Calculator

All Known Implementing Classes:
RevPolishCalc, StandardCalc
public interface Calculator
This is a simple interface that is used in RevPolishCalc and StandardCalc class. It has a abstract method that will be used in both RevPolishCalc and StandardCalc
